WEBVTT

00:07:57.800 --> 00:08:00.776
and sometimes you just,
I don't know, you pee a little bit

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:02.056
when you cough or sneeze,

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:05.256
when you're running upstairs,
or you're stretching.

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:06.816
Don't lie.

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:08.576
It happens. Right?

00:08:08.600 --> 00:08:10.776
She doesn't need to know that, I figure.

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:13.696
(Laughter)

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:18.280
I told her, when you get older,
your bladder is going to grow bigger, too.

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:20.416
When you get old like me,

00:08:20.440 --> 00:08:24.376
you're going to be able
to hold your pee for way longer,

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:25.600
I promised her.

00:08:27.160 --> 00:08:28.800
"Until you can get home?"